			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Initiate_gearchoice3')
			span.sheet-mainbox
			span.sheet-grayable
				span(data-i18n='inititate-gear3') Big sword (3 harm, hand, messy, heavy)
		.sheet-move.sheet-Setting-Default.sheet-Setting-Gothic.sheet-Setting-Dreaming.sheet-Setting-Marches
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Initiate_gearchoice4')
			span.sheet-mainbox
			span.sheet-grayable
				span(data-i18n='inititate-gear4') Big axe (3 harm, hand, messy, slow, heavy)
		.sheet-move.sheet-Setting-Default.sheet-Setting-Gothic.sheet-Setting-Dreaming.sheet-Setting-Marches
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Initiate_gearchoice5')
			span.sheet-mainbox
			span.sheet-grayable
				span(data-i18n='inititate-gear5') Silver knife (1 harm, hand, silver)
